        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Whether “craftily” be the right rendering or not, it is clear that the message was a secret one, for Zebul dissembled his anger until he was strong enough to throw off the mask.",
